Remarks

The conversion from Godot.Collections.Dictionary to Hit2D will be valid when Godot.Collections.Dictionary contains the keys ​​"collider_id", "rid", "metadata" and "collider".

Exceptions

ArgumentNullException

The exception is thrown when Godot.Collections.Dictionary object is null.

InvalidCastException

The exception is called when the Dictionary object is not valid for conversion because it does not contain the keys "collider_id", "rid", "metadata" and "collider".
